div.p:
General. Le Rond suggested alternative solutions;
either the Allies should come to an agreement and when this was done, appoint a
meeting place with the Germans, or they should summon the Germans to Paris.

frus:attachment.p:
The Department of State would like to know if it is desired that the
                        preliminary notice be given by the Department of State or by M. Clemenceau;
                        and desires to know:
